Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.12,0:55:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\blur3\fad(150,150)\alpha&H80&\3c&H81E58B&\1a&HFF&\t(105,150,\1a&H00&)\t(5400,5445,\1a&HFF&)}召唤雏鸟的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.86,0:56:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\blur3\fad(150,150)\alpha&H80&\3c&H81E58B&\1a&HFF&\t(105,150,\1a&H00&)\t(5400,5445,\1a&HFF&)}抬头可见的云朵
